-- Federer Loses Opening Set 6-4 to Tomas Berdych in Wimbledon Quarterfinal
-- James Cone
-- 2010-06-30T12:56:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/federer-loses-opening-set-6-4-to-tomas-berdych-in-wimbledon-quarterfinal.html

          
          
             Top-seed Roger Federer lost the
first set against Tomas Berdych in their Wimbledon quarterfinal
today.  
 Berdych, who has matched his best performance at the only
grass-court Grand Slam, took the opener 6-4.  
          
          


  


        